data.label: Zstandard
data.description: Zstandard，缩写 zstd,是一种快速无损压缩算法，针对 zlib 级别的实时压缩场景以及更好的压缩比。

data.label: Zstandard
data.description: Zstandard, abbreviated as zstd, is a fast lossless compression algorithm aimed at real-time compression scenarios at zlib level and offering better compression ratios.
